            </div>
            <div class="location-card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1477587458883-47145ed94245?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" class="location-image" alt="Himalayan Retreats">
